::Composer::

Composer rubbed his chin with his pointer finger and thumb in thought.

"Well," he said, "I'd be willing to offer to go first, as I wouldn't want
anybody as beautiful as Vamprah, and a member of the Alliance, to be
destroyed and not have my help, but, this is really your choice, Vamprah,
because I don't care if you want to go first or not..."
